{"tid":2388421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[0.5/PR]被揭有大批假帳號操縱社交媒體　華為認有不足展內部調查　Twitter：如證據確鑿不排除永久封鎖","createTime":"2021-01-31T06:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T12:08:09.000Z","uid":51271,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0ea8ad90d363c6ed0b942aecc18dbb9e586e0ef0","tid":2388421,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:18:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%B9%E5%81%87%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F%E6%93%8D%E7%B8%B1%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94-%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E8%AA%8D%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E5%B1%95%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-twitter-%E5%A6%82%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A%E7%A2%BA%E9%91%BF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2581%2587%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E8%2599%259F%25E6%2593%258D%25E7%25B8%25B1%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%25AA%2592%25E9%25AB%2594-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2583%25A8%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-twitter-%25E5%25A6%2582%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2593%259A%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E9%2591%25BF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%2599%25A4%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E4%25B9%2585%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596%2F&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWsjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=6047f07f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2581%2587%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E8%2599%259F%25E6%2593%258D%25E7%25B8%25B1%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%25AA%2592%25E9%25AB%2594-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2583%25A8%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-twitter-%25E5%25A6%2582%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2593%259A%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E9%2591%25BF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%2599%25A4%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E4%25B9%2585%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596%2F&h=36cd14f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%B9%E5%81%87%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F%E6%93%8D%E7%B8%B1%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94-%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E8%AA%8D%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E5%B1%95%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-twitter-%E5%A6%82%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A%E7%A2%BA%E9%91%BF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國際研究機構 Graphika 周四發佈 33 頁的研究報告，指在比利時政府重新審視其 5G 網絡政策，考慮限制華為等「高風險供應商」（high risk vendors）建設該國的 5G 系統期間，社交媒體上出現新一輪操縱行動。首先是出現至少 14 個冒充成電訊專家、作家和學者的 Twitter 帳號分享支持華為的文章，攻擊比利時的新政策。Graphika 分析，雖然這些 Twitter 帳號有個人照片和職業，但照片屬假照片、關注者其實是機器人，相信是假帳號。<br />\n<br />\n為商業利益操弄社交媒體<br />\n<br />\nGraphika 補充，目前沒有證據顯示是誰人操作及資助這些假帳號。不過，這些帳號的帖文獲華為官方帳號及高層轉發，其中華為歐洲官方帳號有超過 500 萬名關注者，分享了 47 條相關推文，令政府、記者和商業領袖等更容易看到這些文章。Graphika 分析員形容，社交媒體的操弄出現了新的變化，有別於如俄羅斯干預 2016 年美國總統大選時是為了實現政治目標，這次是大型跨國公司利用社交平台針對一個歐洲國家，以促進利益的商業操作。<br />\n<br />\n《金融時報》則留意到，至少有 6 名華為在歐洲的員工於去年年初開設帳戶，竟在數星期內吸引了成千上萬的關注者。其中，西歐戰略營銷總裁 Mike Bai 在去年 3 月開設帳戶後，主要只用來分享華為的新聞稿或讚好華為的文章，卻一度有近 90 萬追隨者。據網絡分析公司 Social Blade，其帳戶在去年 4 月中的一個星期，吸引到 16 萬追隨者。"},{"pid":"fa5d21ab955f6c0693ac72e00588e005346c8d33","tid":2388421,"uid":7369,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:23:42.000Z","msg":"扮乜撚嘢，係人都知支那搞鬼啦"},{"pid":"814fc21be7968a81437d812a74e6133d3feba6d9","tid":2388421,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:24:11.000Z","msg":"★支那好治癒gif貼圖區！（9）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2251420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2251420</a><br />\n<br />\n無尾bear快入"},{"pid":"7cf819b9ffde83f851952c5075ed65c3e3e5d54d","tid":2388421,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"814fc21be7968a814